name: Spring Heeled Jack’s guide to the pleasures of horrific terror: Pt. 1 – tearing the fingernails from crying children
description:
“Contrary to popular belief, maximum effect can be gained by starting slowly, tearing horizontally, and increasing the application of pressure-per-square-inch in conjunction with the level of decibels of the child’s screaming

“If you’re like me, you’ll come to appreciate the sound over time but if you’re a beginner, I advise a calming hum to bracket the cat-like cry”

4000 x 2734 PNG
